---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Acceptable Use Policy — MotionMax"
  description="MotionMax acceptable use policy. Understand the permitted and prohibited uses of our AI video generation platform."
  canonical="https://motionmax.io/acceptable-use"
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-2">Acceptable Use Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-10">Last updated: February 2026</p>

  <div class="space-y-8 text-muted-foreground">

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">1. Overview</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">MotionMax provides AI-powered video generation tools. By using our platform, you agree to use it responsibly and in accordance with this Acceptable Use Policy ("AUP"). Violations may result in account suspension or termination.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">2. Prohibited Content</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">You may not use MotionMax to create or distribute content that:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Is illegal, harmful, threatening, abusive, harassing, or defamatory</li>
        <li>Infringes any intellectual property rights of any third party</li>
        <li>Contains explicit, pornographic, or sexually explicit material</li>
        <li>Promotes violence, terrorism, or self-harm</li>
        <li>Spreads disinformation, deepfakes, or misleading content designed to deceive</li>
        <li>Violates the privacy of any individual without consent</li>
        <li>Targets or harasses specific individuals or groups</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">3. Voice Cloning</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">The voice cloning feature requires your explicit consent and must only be used with voices you have the legal right to clone. Cloning another person's voice without their explicit written consent is strictly prohibited and may constitute a violation of applicable laws, including those related to fraud, identity theft, and defamation.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">4. Commercial Use</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">Commercial use of generated videos is permitted under paid plans. You are responsible for ensuring that content you distribute commercially complies with all applicable laws and does not infringe third-party rights.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">5. API &amp; Automation</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">Automated access, scraping, or reverse engineering of MotionMax's systems is prohibited without explicit written permission. Rate limits must be respected at all times.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">6. Enforcement</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">We reserve the right to remove content, suspend, or permanently terminate accounts that violate this policy, without prior notice. Repeated violations will result in permanent bans without refund.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">7. Reporting Violations</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">To report a violation of this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:abuse@motionmax.io" class="text-primary hover:underline">abuse@motionmax.io</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="border-t border-border/30 pt-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm">
        Questions? <a href="mailto:support@motionmax.io" class="text-primary hover:underline">Contact us</a>
        &nbsp;·&nbsp;
        <a href="/terms" class="text-primary hover:underline">Terms</a>
        &nbsp;·&nbsp;
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy</a>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</LegalLayout>
